{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or-- there was a lady with-- with her son, and I think her husband already was dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't even remember the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she of course was older, so she tried to sort of, you know, look after us, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wasn't [INAUDIBLE] she was very sick herself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at one time or another, you know, when we went out, one of the soldiers would approach me and said, where are you from, and-- in German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, from Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, I'll take you back tomorrow to Holland, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted to, you know-- to be nice to us, you know, all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they didn't-- you know, they wanted to maybe-- that's the thing-- that's the solution for these poor kids, you know, running around, nothing to eat and-- and looked terrible.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So of course, he couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, I mean, this officer wouldn't allow that, and, I mean, can't just arbitrarily start taking people back, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed there for about two weeks, I would say, in-- in-- in this little town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried to take care of us as well as they could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even for the lice-- we didn't get rid of the lice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tried to get medicine for the typhus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tried to feed us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this is-- was the most important thing, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you to fight disease, you have to feed the people also, first of all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did, you know, try to find food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At least I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was so sick that I really couldn't eat, which was good because most-- many people overate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, your body is no longer used to eating rich foods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some of them, you know, went into houses and saw meat lying there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they ate it, took it and they-- all meat [INAUDIBLE] they ate it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] got very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I couldn't really eat any food, so I ate some-- I remember eating mostly bread, dry bread, or biscuits.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was-- that's what I ate, and that's what also helped me to survive because my digestive system didn't-- wasn't put under that strain, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after about 10 days to two weeks, the Americans decided to-- OK, these are mostly Dutch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were some other people on the train with us, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They stayed behind, probably.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were not Dutch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we were mostly Dutch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were going to take us back to Holland because, you know, the-- there were other DPs in the area, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "DPs are displaced persons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They-- they didn't-- they had to put them up in camps, you know, and if they could repatriate people, the better, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And some of these people were-- really wanted to get back to Holland because they were Dutch, you know, and maybe they had family there or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were put on a-- unfortunately, they had no rolling stuff, nothing decent, so they put it on this open wagons.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, those-- that they carry, say, a trailer-- it seemed like-- like open trailers we were put on, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to travel only by day, and by night they put us up somewhere on the way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they fed us, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it didn't-- didn't help because it was sort of-- even if it was April, it seemed very hot to me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we were in the open sun, you know, and-- and I got very sick on the way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that we never-- I never had enough water, and I needed water to drink, and there never was enough water because we were traveling.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't have any bottles or anything like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after about three days, we got to-- to Maastricht, to Holland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And most of the-- the major part of Holland, as a matter of fact, had only been liberated when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was isolated from the rest of-- from the rest of Europe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a-- like a fortress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You ?] called it Fortress Holland, and-- and the Germans held it until the very end.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Maastricht was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they were liberated then, and at that-- everything-- the Americans had everything there, and a lot of hospitals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was very sick by the time we got there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the rest of the people-- most-- many of the people were taken off the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
